The greenhouse has a clear, translucent roof and walls, and the woman is framed by an open window. A sign that says "VEGAN CRAP" is visible on the top of the greenhouse. The woman is wearing a black blazer over a pink shirt.
The Instagram post by veganish_crap shows a video of their garden, specifically focusing on carrot tops. The caption says "Garden update!".
The image shows a squash growing on a vine, likely in a garden or backyard. The caption indicates that the squashes are "coming in hot," suggesting a recent harvest or upcoming harvest.

The image shows a close-up of a freshly baked loaf of bread on a wire rack. The words "Good Morning" are written on the bread in purple. The caption indicates the poster is vegan and the hashtags suggest a focus on plant-based cooking, healthy eating, and food photography.

The image is an Instagram post featuring a homemade spicy tomato soup and grilled cheese sandwich. The caption mentions the grilled cheese was made with homemade bread from @ranchers_pizzeria_bar and the soup recipe is from @forksoverknives. The post is tagged with various vegan and plant-based hashtags.

The image is an Instagram post by veganish_crap featuring a pot of chickpea curry with spinach and cauliflower, served with a side of rice. The caption mentions homemade naan and credits @pinchofyum and @nora_cooks_vegan_ for the recipe.
